import React from 'react'

export const LoadingScreen = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      class="spinner"
      width="65px"
      height="65px"
      viewBox="0 0 66 66"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <circle
        class="path"
        fill="none"
        stroke-width="6"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        cx="33"
        cy="33"
        r="30"
      ></circle>
    </svg>
  )
}
